Provides: electronic-medical-record
Description: Australian electronic medical record, client package.
 A native graphical client for the EasyGP electronic medical record.
 .
 Features include:
   * Prescribing
   * Problem list optionally using various coding systems
   * WorkCover
   * Careplans
   * Vaccinations

Package: easygp-server-empty
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, postgresql (>= 9.1), postgresql-contrib (>= 9.1), cron, postgresql-plpython-9.4 | postgresql-plython-9.3 | postgresql-plython-9.1 | postgresql-plpython, python-psycopg2
Description: Australian electronic medical record, server package
 All dependencies required for an EasyGP database server, plus the Python scripts for Medicare Online/PCEHR, plus the update scripts.
 However does NOT install a database. Suitable for developers or building a system to restore from backup
 .
 EasyGP itself is a fully-featured electronic medical record
 with a graphical native client written in Gambas.

